description: Attention first-time buyers and/or empty nesters looking to downsize: see this spacious (809 SF) one-bedroom condo with deeded parking. This unit is one of twelve units in a well-maintained building that has undergone recent updates, ensuring its excellent condition. The roof was updated in 2018, the siding in 2017, and the driveway will be repaved this month (Sept.). The open floor plan features an updated kitchen and bathroom, as well as the convenience of an in-unit washer and dryer. Step outside to your private, gated patio—perfect for entertaining—which leads directly to your deeded end-unit parking space. With two private entrances, this home offers a townhouse-style feel. Additional perks include a massive private storage unit and easy access to the building’s amenities. Conveniently located just a short walk to the Broadway T Stop, West Broadway shops & restaurants, and minutes to the Seaport & Financial District.
